Version 0.15
------------
2010-Feb-18:	Update translation files.
2010-Feb-17:	Add support for PHP 5.3 (Zend API 20090626).
2010-Feb-17:	Remove support of very old ZEND API version.
2010-Feb-17:	Clenup code (reference to PHP4 unsupported).
2010-Feb-16:	Change declaration of variable for use globals.
2010-Feb-16:	Fix database loading when it isn't in the default directory.
2010-Feb-10:	Minor fix of variables declaration.
2010-Feb-10:	Remove phpapi-20060613 debian dependency.
2009-Dec-09:	Add phpclamav_test.php for testing function and valid is extension is correctly loaded.
2009-Dec-08:	Change defaults values in the clamav.ini with the correct default ClamAV values.
2009-Dec-08:    Suppress clamav.archivememlim parameters that no longuer support by clamav 0.95.x.
2009-Dec-08:    Update documentation.
2009-Dec-08:    Add clamav.maxscansize parameters.
2009-Dec-07:    Fix security bug that doesn't scan file bigger than ~20MB.
2009-Dec-07:    Show loaded parameters on php_info().
2009-Dec-07:    cl_scanfile() now return the result of ClamAV function.
2009-Dec-07:    cl_scanfile() now return the virus name if found in a parameters.
2009-Dec-07:    Suppress cl_scanfile_ex() function.
2009-Dec-07:    Cleanup code.

